    <p>The natural <i>5</i> Kf3 fails after <i>5</i> . . . Re8 <i>6</i> Kf4, Rg8 <i>7</i> Kf5, Rxg7, and the Rook giving up his life for the second Pawn, draws for Black.</p>
    
