    <p>The alternative is <i>1</i> . . . Kh2 <i>2</i> Nxh4, Kh3 <i>3</i> Nf5, h5 <i>4</i> Kgl, h4 (unfortunately forced) <i>5</i> gxh4, and the Rook Pawn marches up the board to Queen.</p>
    
