    <p>There is no hope in 5. . . Kh3 <i>6</i> Kf3, and Black must abandon the Pawn, nor in <i>5</i> . . . Kg4 <i>6</i> Kf2, h3 <i>7</i> Rh7, and again the Pawn falls.</p>
    
